		<title>Candidate-press relations are, well, about as ‘sour’ as usual</title>
		<link>http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/reuters/blogs/JackShafer/~3/Xr9Qq7nJNq8/</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.reuters.com/jackshafer/2012/05/16/candidate-press-relations-are-about-as-sour-as-usual/#comments</comments>
